%N A395321 Decimal expansion of the conjecturally maximum possible volume of a polyhedron with 16 vertices inscribed in the unit sphere.
%C A395321 Due to the high symmetry of the arrangement of the vertices (symmetry group S4 with order 24), there is hope that an analytical representation of this constant exists, but this is not yet known.
%H A395321 Hugo Pfoertner, <a href="https://www.randomwalk.de/sphere/volmax/pages/16.htm">Visualization of Polyhedron</a>, (1999).
